<DATE>01/16/2008</DATE>
<AUTHOR>hoss</AUTHOR>
<TEXT>I bought this dark red 'program car' as an ex-rental with ~10,000 miles on it in December '07. A certified used LT 2007 for $16,000. Great savings off of new and I don't particularly like the looks of the 2008. I love it so much more than the other cars I test drove (new foreign sub- compacts). Quality is on par and you get so much more for your money. Styling is great; mpg decent for V6 power; comfort; utilitarian design; safety features.</TEXT>
<FAVORITE>Practical, hatchback, heated seats, XM, rear moonroof, tight quality feel</FAVORITE>
